quran[42{c,v,t}:
80,1,"tursh ro howa, aur be rukhi Barti"
80,2,iss baat par ke woh andha uss ke paas aa gaya
80,3,"tumhe kya khabar, shayad woh sudhar jaye"
80,4,"ya nasiyaat par dheyaan day, aur nasiyaat karna is ke liye nafea ho ?"
80,5,jo shakhs be parwai brtta hai
80,6,is ki taraf to tum tavajja karte ho
80,7,halaank agar woh nah sudhray tu tum par is ki kya zimma daari hai ?
80,8,aur jo khud tumahray paas dora aata hai
80,9,aur woh dar raha hota hai
80,10,is se tum be rukhi brtte ho
80,11,"hargiz nahi, yeh to aik nasiyaat hai"
80,12,jis ka jee chahay isay qubool kere
80,13,yeh aisay saheefon mein darj hai jo mukaram hain
80,14,"buland martaba hain, pakeeza hain"
80,15,Muaziz aur naik katobon ke
80,16,hathon mein rehtay hain
80,17,"laanat ho ensaan par, kaisa sakht munkir haq hai yeh"
80,18,kis cheez se Allah ne isay peda kya hai ?
80,19,"nutfa ki aik boond se Allah ne isay peda kya, phir iss ki taqdeer muqarrar ki"
80,20,phir iss ke liye zindagi ki raah aasaan ki
80,21,phir isay mout di aur qabar mein pohanchaya
80,22,phir jab chahay woh isay dobarah utha khara kere
80,23,"hargiz nahi, iss ne woh farz ada nahi kya jis ka Allah ne isay hukum diya tha"
80,24,phir zara ensaan apni khoraak ko dekhe
80,25,hum ne khoob pani lundhaya
80,26,phir zameen ko ajeeb terhan phara
80,27,phir uss ke andar ugaye ghallay
80,28,aur angoor aur tarkariyan
80,29,aur Zaitoon aur khjorin
80,30,aur ghany baagh
80,31,"aur terhan terhan ke phal, aur chaaray"
80,32,tumahray liye aur tumahray maweshion ke liye samaan zeist ke tor par
80,33,aakhir kaar jab woh kaan behray kar dainay wali aawaz buland hogi
80,34,uss roz aadmi apne bhai
80,35,aur apni maa aur apne baap
80,36,aur apni biwi aur apni aulaad se bhage ga
80,37,un mein se har shakhs par is din aisa waqt aa parre ga ke usay apne siwa kisi ka hosh nah hoga
80,38,kuch chehray uss roz damak rahay hon ge
80,39,hashash bashaash aur khush o Khurram hon ge
80,40,aur kuch cheharon par is roz khaak urr rahi hogi
80,41,aur clons(siyahi) chhai hui hogi
80,42,yahi kafir o fajir log hon ge
